description: List provisioned resources for a service instance with details.

parameters.name: serviceInstanceName
parameters.description: The name of the service instance whose provisioned resources you want.

parameters.name: serviceName
parameters.description: The name of the service that serviceInstanceName is associated to.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates the location of the next provisioned resource in the array of provisioned resources, after the current requested list of provisioned resources.

nested_items.name: provisionedResources
nested_items.description: An array of provisioned resources for a service instance.

nested_items.name: provisioningEngine
nested_items.description: The resource provisioning engine. At this time, CLOUDFORMATION can be used for Amazon Web Services-managed provisioning, and TERRAFORM can be used for self-managed provisioning.
